## Design Tokens & Theme System

### Current Tokens (defined in `globals.css`)

```css
:root {
  --background: #ffffff;
  --foreground: #171717;
}

@theme inline {
  --color-background: var(--background);
  --color-foreground: var(--foreground);
  --font-sans: var(--font-geist-sans);
  --font-mono: var(--font-geist-mono);
}

@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
  :root {
    --background: #141d2c;
    --foreground: #ededed;
  }
}
```

### Token Usage Rules

- **Always use tokens**: `bg-background`, `text-foreground`, `font-sans`, `font-mono`
- **Extend, don't override**: Add new tokens to `@theme inline` for brand colors, spacing scales, etc.
- **Avoid arbitrary values**: `bg-[#123456]` or `w-[37px]` should be rare exceptions
- **Semantic naming**: Use purpose-based names (`--color-primary`, `--color-danger`) not descriptive (`--color-blue-500`)

### Adding New Tokens

