### Performance Considerations

- Tailwind purges unused classes in production automatically
- Avoid dynamic class construction: `text-${size}` (won't be purged correctly)
- Use complete class names: `text-sm`, `text-base`, `text-lg`
- For dynamic values, use inline styles or CSS variables

